+ "Stop &Form"          KillModule FvwmForm
+ "Stop &Identify"     	KillModule FvwmIdent
+ "Stop &ScrollBar"    	KillModule FvwmScroll
+ "Stop Sound Event"    KillModule FvwmEvent
+ "Stop Auto Rais&e"   	KillModule FvwmAuto

